                            </cit> <ref cRef="Sx. Masc." loc="29 Enc.">Sx. Masc. 29 Enc.</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወዐለ፡ ቅድሜሁ፡ ሞት፡</foreign> (lictoris vel stipatoris instar, <lbl expand="videas">vid.</lbl> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወዓሊ፡</foreign>) <foreign xml:lang="grc">τρέχει</foreign> <ref cRef="Job" loc="41,13">Job 41,13</ref>.</sense> <sense n="2" xml:id="D2"> in specie: <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
